        <message_html><![CDATA[<div style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5; color: #333333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; border-radius: 8px; background-color: #ffffff;"><!-- Header banner -->
<div style="background-color: #1a365d; color: #ffffff; padding: 15px; border-radius: 6px 6px 0 0; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold;">Workspace Inspection Required</div>
<!-- Main Body Text -->
<p style="margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px;">A workspace reservation has been checked out and requires your inspection.</p>
<!-- Record Details Card -->
<div style="background-color: #f7fafc; border: 1px solid #edf2f7; border-radius: 6px; padding: 15px; margin-bottom: 25px;">
<table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td style="padding: 4px 0; font-weight: bold; width: 35%; color: #4a5568;">Reservation:</td>
<td style="padding: 4px 0; color: #1a202c;">${number}</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="padding: 4px 0; font-weight: bold; color: #4a5568;">Workspace:</td>
<td style="padding: 4px 0; color: #1a202c;">${workspace}</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="padding: 4px 0; font-weight: bold; color: #4a5568;">Reservation Status:</td>
<td style="padding: 4px 0; color: #1a202c;"><span style="background-color: #feebc8; color: #c05621; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: bold;">${reservation_status}</span></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<!-- Instructions Section -->
<p style="margin-bottom: 12px; font-weight: bold; color: #2d3748;">Please inspect the workspace area now that the session has ended.</p>
<ul style="margin: 0; padding-left: 20px; color: #4a5568;">
<li style="margin-bottom: 10px;">If no issues are found, no further action is needed.</li>
<li style="margin-bottom: 10px;"><strong>If maintenance is required:</strong>
<ol style="margin-top: 6px; margin-bottom: 0; padding-left: 20px; color: #2d3748;">
<li style="margin-bottom: 4px;">Open the reservation record</li>
<li style="margin-bottom: 4px;">Fill out the <em>Maintenance issue</em> field</li>
<li style="margin-bottom: 4px;">Save the record</li>
<li style="margin-bottom: 4px;">Set the <em>Reservation status</em> to <strong>Needs Maintenance</strong></li>
</ol>
</li>
</ul>
<!-- Footer --><hr style="border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #edf2f7; margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
<p style="font-size: 12px; color: #718096; margin: 0;">Thank you,<br><strong>Workspace Reservation Management System</strong></p>
</div>]]></message_html>
